00:21:29.319 --> 00:21:30.520
that comes here.

00:21:30.520 --> 00:21:37.640
Or could be any other decoration to the existing module that it will look the way you need

00:21:37.640 --> 00:21:43.719
in your company or you'd like to then to your stakeholders to utilize this.

00:21:44.280 --> 00:21:48.439
This, of course, will be, this can go way further.

00:21:48.439 --> 00:21:54.199
And with this example, this is exactly the same TL module association where you can even

00:21:54.199 --> 00:21:56.839
change the type of the output if you like.

00:21:56.839 --> 00:22:01.319
So this is still association between race and the biomarker.

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:06.760
And we can see this, how it might work.

00:22:06.760 --> 00:22:15.239
So, of course, based on this, we might, of course, thinking about them, does size fits

00:22:15.239 --> 00:22:15.959
all?

