And I believe with the extension, with your work, with your contribution, you might bring

00:22:25.239 --> 00:22:35.560
different new capabilities, new functionalities that we all can build one solution that really

00:22:36.280 --> 00:22:38.599
fits to all of us in the future.

00:22:38.599 --> 00:22:42.359
As an example, of course, we can go even further.

