00:40:43.239 --> 00:40:51.239
I think, I might guess, but I think it would be great if we start to speak the same language,

00:40:51.239 --> 00:40:56.280
the same, I don't know, safety output looks the same across the industry, right?

00:40:56.280 --> 00:40:59.239
