00:40:59.239 --> 00:41:06.840
So those are big opportunities, advantages to working together, but also moving out from

00:41:06.840 --> 00:41:13.159
what probably for last, at least I can see for last 25 years being industry that we used

00:41:13.159 --> 00:41:16.120
to work a lot in a silo on a solution.

00:41:16.120 --> 00:41:24.439
