00:46:00.760 --> 00:46:06.280
So Sumesh touched on it, but the way that we're doing this is through containerization.

00:46:06.280 --> 00:46:12.439
So packages come in, like users say, hey, I need package XYZ.

00:46:12.439 --> 00:46:14.120
We evaluate the risk of that.

00:46:14.120 --> 00:46:15.719
